description:
This is a 20 minute workout called '20 Minute Guided Meditation for Manifesting Your Desired Reality' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is an Original 20 minute manifesting guided meditation recorded by us.  May you wake up feeling grateful for this new day and the endless possibilities it holds.  May you be open to receiving all the positive energy, abundance, and blessings that the universe has in store for you.  May your thoughts, words, and actions be aligned with your highest good and the good of all beings. It's our wish for you to trust in the universe's guidance and know that everything is unfolding perfectly for you.  Remember that you are loved and supported, and everything you need is already within you.  Let's make today amazing and manifest your desired reality!

A special thank you to all our monthly supporters!  
We appreciate all your support and contribution to allow this channel to continue to share our guided meditations with the world.  Thank you!!!
If you would like to join our monthly supporters, you can do so here:  https://www.buymeacoffee.com/greatmeditation/membership
